OL,3,CThousands attend anti-racism rally in
OL,4,CBelfast
OL,6,FSeveral attendees at the rally held
OL,7,Fplacards reading slogans such as:
OL,8,F"Racists go home", and: "The problem
OL,9,Fis evil and violence, not race".
